# Format: Name=URL
# The live file is ../syno-mihomo-gateway-data/config/subscription.txt (seeded by
# bootstrap.sh / the installer - OUTSIDE the release tree, so your token is never
# committed and survives release-directory replacement). Paste your real URL there.
# The mihomo entrypoint uses the FIRST valid (non-#) line found.
# Example:
MyAirport=https://provider.example/api/v1/subscribe?token=REPLACE_ME
